      <title>印度银行业流动性赤字创六个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/indian-banking-liquidity-deficit-hits-highest-in-six-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于企业提前缴纳税款以及央行为抑制卢比波动而可能抛售美元，印度银行系统的流动性赤字达到近六个月来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/indian-banking-liquidity-deficit-hits-highest-in-six-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 08:55:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
